This is a Soccer Field/ Stadiuim prefab made by nosoul!

There is the field part, then there is the small ring around the field, then there are the seats. 

The seating part isnt meant to be played one(there is nodraw still visible)

There is prexisting lighting that I made but you can change that if you want. 

You will need to add spawn points(there is one which i used for testing)

There is a light_environment and a env_sun


If you use this, please give credit to me :)

Enjoy!

Extract to your:
C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\user name\sourcesdk_content\cstrike\mapsrc
